versions.correctionNotice:
Quarterly growth rates for real household disposable income (RHDI) per head 

Errors have been identified in the quarterly growth rates for real household disposable income (RHDI) per head in Table 1.1.5. Data from 1955 to 2015 are affected, impacting the following two series;

DU8Y Real disposable income at chained volume prices, percentage change, latest quarter on previous quarter 

DU8Z Real disposable income at chained volume prices, percentage change, latest quarter on corresponding quarter of previous year 

These errors have now been corrected. No other series have been affected. 

ONS apologises for any inconvenience caused.
